        * dom/InProcessMessagePortChannel.h:

        * dom/MessagePort.cpp:
        (WebCore::MessagePort::dispatchMessages):
        * dom/MessagePortChannel.h:

2018-01-02  Jiewen Tan  <jiewen_tan@apple.com>

